track_notes: This ones a true joy. Take the family. Parking, easy slope, maintained trail, open summit, views.

An easy 1.9 mile/900 EG hike on one of the best maintained trails around. Plenty of parking available at the state park. Open space on the summit is somewhat limited and is a pretty high traffic area.
Just thought I would do a track on the service rd. just for reference. Probably would not use it unless I was in a hurry to get down.
